Package: rpathsonpaths
Type: Package
Title: Simulate population genetics of foodborne diseases
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Martin", "Hinsch", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="hinsch.martin@gmail.com"),
			person("Thibaut", "Jombart", role=c("ctb")))
Description: Rpathsonpaths is a population genetics simulator for foodborne diseases. It 
	provides methods to simulate how infections spread on a food transport network and what
	the genetic structure of an outbreak will look like.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: methods, utils, Rcpp (>= 0.12.9)
Suggests: igraph, knitr, rmarkdown, testthat, outbreaks, epicontacts
LinkingTo: Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++11
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/mhinsch/rpathsonpaths
BugReports: https://github.com/mhinsch/rpathsonpaths/issues

